channel.title: Help with title
channel.description: okay so i'm working on editing a client but i was wondering how do you edit at the very top where it says the old clients name? i can't figure it out much appreciated

item.title: Help with title
item.dc:creator: @birdman4657 birdman4657
item.description:
@birdman4657 wrote:

ok go into your Gui.java

search for: frameTitle = (usually at the bottom)

and change whatever is in the " " to your client name > compile

heres an example of mine:

public static String frameTitle = "The Armageddon - Experience";
